npm  i bcryptjs cors dotenv express express-validator jsonwebtoken mongoose multer  pdf-parse  @google/genai
AI-Powered Learning Assistant App-এর জন্য package গুলোর short use case:

| Package             | Use Case                                                           |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| `express`           | Backend API server তৈরি                                            |
| `cors`              | React frontend ↔ Express backend connection                        |
| `dotenv`            | API keys, database URI, secrets secure রাখা                        |
| `mongoose`          | MongoDB database connect ও data model তৈরি                         |
| `bcryptjs`          | User password hash করা                                             |
| `jsonwebtoken`      | Login authentication token তৈরি                                    |
| `express-validator` | Signup/Login/Input validation                                      |
| `multer`            | PDF, notes, assignments upload করা                                 |
| `pdf-parse`         | PDF থেকে text extract করা                                          |
| `@google/genai`     | Gemini AI ব্যবহার করে chat, summary, Q&A, explanation generate করা |

### Example Flow

1. User Signup/Login

   * `bcryptjs`
   * `jsonwebtoken`
   * `express-validator`

2. User PDF Upload

   * `multer`

3. PDF Read

   * `pdf-parse`

4. Send PDF Content to Gemini

   * `@google/genai`

5. Save Chat History/User Data

   * `mongoose`

6. Serve APIs

   * `express`

7. Connect Frontend

   * `cors`

8. Store Secrets

   * `dotenv`

এই package set দিয়ে তুমি AI Learning Assistant-এর features বানাতে পারবে যেমন:

* AI Tutor Chat
* PDF Summarizer
* Question Answering
* Notes Explanation
* Quiz Generation
* Study Assistant
* User Authentication
* Chat History Storage


